-- Seed data: 110 customers drawn from 20 first names x 15 last names via a
-- coprime stride over the 300-combo Cartesian product so every row is a
-- distinct (first, last) pair. created_at spans roughly the last year (oldest
-- first); every 10th row has a modified_at more recent than created_at,
-- simulating recent edits. Loaded via spring.datasource.data at startup.


-- Vehicle seed: every customer has 1 or 2 vehicles (customers without cars would
-- not be visiting an auto shop). Customers whose id is a multiple of 3 get two.
-- VINs are fake but conform to the 17-char length rule.

-- Vehicle rows inserted: 146
